HEADWORD: Stoner
<hw>Ston"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
stones; one who makes an assault with stones.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who walls with stones.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

